00:13:25,424 --> 00:13:27,688
Yeah. Now look, the manager there's
gonna put up a stink

224
00:13:27,726 --> 00:13:28,954
but he knows the drill.

225
00:13:28,994 --> 00:13:30,393
- Nothing you can't handle.
